  <brief_title>Comparison of Automatic CPAP to Fixed CPAP for OSAS Following a Prediction Formula</brief_title>
  <official_title>Titration Efficacy of Automatic CPAP Versus Fixed CPAP, Following a Prediction Formula in Patients With OSAS</official_title>
  <sponsors>
