  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with proven Obstructive Sleep Apnea Syndrome

          -  Apnea-hypopnea-index &gt; 20/h

          -  Awaking index &gt; 30/h

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe nasal obstruction

          -  Hypoventilation

          -  Excessive sleep fragmentation caused by non-respiratory factors

          -  COPD (FEV1/FVC &lt; 65%)

          -  CPAP compliance &lt; 3h per night

          -  Insufficient sleep time (&lt; 2h TST) during one of both parts of the split night
             CPAP-titration

          -  Patients needing &gt; 16 mbar CPAP pressures
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
